# Writing Style

## Tone
- Factual and concise. Every sentence should convey information.
- No filler phrases. No speculation.
- Use active voice.

## Dates
- Always use YYYY-MM-DD format
- In prose: "discussed on 2026-02-23"

## Links
Use standard markdown links. All paths are relative to vault root with .md extension.
Never use [[wikilinks]].

## Structure
1. H1 title
2. Tag line
3. Content with H2/H3 headings

## Missing Data
- Omit empty sections rather than writing placeholders
- Never fabricate names, dates, or facts
